data.description: Welcome Home to 719 Rock Springs Road! This home features three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, a large living room that is open to the beautiful kitchen and dining area! Off of the dining area is large deck that overlooks your private backyard. Sitting on .67 acre you are going to love this level yard that provides some shade trees. If you love convenience, then you will love living here! You are less than 5 minutes to everything Easley has to offer! You are directly across the street from Smithfield Golf Course! Schedule your appointment today! You do not want to miss the opportunity of owning this wonderful home!
